# 📱 Mobile Sales Dashboard – Power BI Project

![Mobile Sales Dashboard](dashboard_preview.png)
## 📌 Project Overview
The **Mobile Sales Dashboard** is an interactive Power BI project developed to analyze mobile phone sales performance across brands, cities, payment methods, and time periods.
This dashboard transforms raw sales data into meaningful business insights through dynamic visualizations, KPI tracking, and interactive filtering, helping stakeholders make data-driven decisions.

## 🎯 Objectives
- Analyze overall mobile sales performance
- Track monthly and daily sales trends
- Compare sales across mobile brands
- Evaluate customer rating distribution
- Understand customer payment preferences
- Identify top-performing cities and regions

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- **Power BI Desktop**
- **Power Query**
- **DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)**
- **Data Modeling**
- **Microsoft Excel (Data Source)**

## 📊 Dashboard Features

### 🔹 KPI Metrics
✔ Total Sales  
✔ Total Quantity Sold  
✔ Total Transactions  
✔ Average Price  

### 🔹 Interactive Filters
- Brand
- Mobile Model
- Payment Method
- Month Selection
- Clear All Filters

### 🔹 Visualizations
- Transaction Analysis by Payment Method (Pie Chart)
- Quantity Distribution by City (Map)
- Sales by Mobile Model (Bar Chart)
- Customer Rating Distribution (Funnel Chart)
- Sales Trend by Day (Line Chart)
- Quantity Trend by Month (Line Chart)
- Brand-wise Sales & Transactions Table---

## 📈 Key Insights
- Generated insights from **₹769M+ Total Sales**
- Identified top-performing mobile models
- Evaluated customer satisfaction trends
- Compared payment method preferences
- Tracked monthly and weekday sales performance
- Analyzed city-wise demand distribution

## 🧮 DAX Measures

```DAX
Total Sales =
SUM(Sales[Total_Sales])

Total Quantity =
SUM(Sales[Quantity])

Total Transactions =
COUNT(Sales[Transaction_ID])

Average Price =
DIVIDE([Total Sales], [Total Quantity])

## 🗂️ Data Model
The dashboard follows a structured data model connecting:
- Sales Data
- Product Information
- Customer Ratings
- Payment Details
- Geographic Data

